browse to directory and type :  pod init 
a podfile will be created
open the podfile and add  (pod 'name of the pod' , '~> 2.0') after the target 'app name' 
back to terminal type : pod install
then from now on use the projectname.xcworkspace file to open the project instead of the projectname.xcodeproj

